        "text_GWtt3M": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2><strong>Warranty Coverage</strong></h2><p>All RŌ products are covered by a <strong>3-year limited warranty</strong> from the date of purchase.</p><ul><li>This warranty covers <strong>defects in materials and workmanship</strong> under normal use.</li><li>Individual <strong>components and accessories</strong> are covered for a period of <strong>1 year</strong> from the date of purchase.</li></ul><h2><strong>What is Covered</strong></h2><p>This warranty applies to:</p><ul><li>Manufacturing defects in materials</li><li>Faulty construction or workmanship</li></ul><h2><strong>What is Not Covered</strong></h2><p>This warranty does not cover:</p><ul><li>Normal wear and tear</li><li>Cosmetic damage (scratches, fading, stains, etc.)</li><li>Damage caused by misuse, neglect, accidents, or improper care</li><li>Unauthorized repairs or modifications</li></ul><h2><strong>Making a Warranty Claim</strong></h2><p>To submit a warranty claim, you must provide:</p><ul><li>Proof of purchase</li><li>Clear photographs of the defect</li><li>A detailed description of the issue</li></ul><p>RŌ reserves the right to request additional information where necessary.</p><h2><strong>Product Inspection</strong></h2><p>In certain circumstances, RŌ may require the product to be <strong>returned for inspection</strong> before a claim can be processed. Instructions will be provided if this is required.</p><h2><strong>Retailer & Distributor Purchases</strong></h2><p>If your product was purchased through a <strong>retailer or distributor</strong>, all warranty claims must be made <strong>directly with the original place of purchase</strong>. They will handle the claim in accordance with RŌ’s warranty policy.</p><h2><strong>Resolution</strong></h2><p>If a defect is confirmed and covered under this warranty, RŌ will, at its discretion:</p><ul><li>Repair the product, or</li><li>Replace the product with the same or comparable item</li></ul><p>This warranty gives you specific legal rights, and you may also have other rights which vary by region.</p><p>For further assistance, please contact RŌ customer support.</p>"
          }
        },
